doc.previous: Tennessee has a rich variety of public private charter and specialized education facilities ranging from pre school through university education
doc.after: Public higher education is under the oversight of the Tennessee Higher Education Commission which provides guidance to two public university systems the University of Tennessee system and the Tennessee Board of Regents In addition a number of private colleges and universities are located throughout the state
